* When Partitioning\nApplies
** Table Size Thresholds
***_ < 1 TB → Don't partition
***_ > 1 TB → Consider partitioning
***_ Each partition ≥ 1 GB
** Benefits at Scale
***_ Partition pruning
***_ Parallel processing per partition
***_ Reduce data scanned
** Small Tables
***_ Ingestion time clustering auto-applied
***_ Partition overhead outweighs benefits
** Very Large Tables (100s TB)
***_ Partitioning delivers greatest benefit
@endmindmap
